%N A021344 Expansion of 1/((1-x)*(1-3*x)*(1-4*x)*(1-5*x)).
%C A021344 Sum of products 1^(p1)*3^(p2)*4^(p3)*5^(p4) where p1+p2+p3+p4=n, pi nonnegative integers _Enrique Navarrete_, Mar 21 2026
